<quantity box="[1159,1234,440,464]" metricMagnitude="2" metricUnit="m" metricValue="4.97" pageId="9" unit="m" value="497.0">497 m</quantity>
, and suppOrting a great variatiOn Of temperature Of 4.9 °C tO 17.2 °C. Thus, this the first repOrt Of 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Smith" authorityYear="1881" box="[1060,1218,476,500]" class="Malacostraca" family="Crangonidae" genus="Pontophilus" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Decapoda" pageId="9" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="brevirostris">
<emphasis box="[1060,1218,476,500]" italics="true" pageId="9">P. brevirostris</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
frOm sOuthwestern Atlantic (Brazilian waters).
